Instructions for running the application

=================================
   when running on an already existing database 

 1. update concepts in database, ----only concepts!!
 2. run script/activate_triggers.sql to activate triggers so you can view report figures
 3. run the sql script in db/migrate/create_site_wards.sql 

================================

    when running on a new database
	check that db/migrate/concepts has latest concepts

 1. run mysql -u root -p database < db/migrate/concepts.sql
 2. run mysql -u root -p database < db/relationship_type.sql
 2. run script/initial_database_setup.sh your_environment your_site
